author: Praveen Menon
title: New Zealand wakes up to eerie silence as coronavirus lockdown begins
description: New Zealand started a one-month compulsory lockdown on Thursday to slow the spread of the coronavirus, with warnings from authorities to stay at home or face huge fines and even jail time.
content:
